ng. The gunman killed six fathers that day, all of them leaving behind their children far too soon. &lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;Let's follow the President's lead so more kids won't have to experience a day like September 27th.&lt;br \/&gt;<\/p>\n<\/div><nav class=\"sharing\">\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"facebook\">\n            <div class=\"fb-like\" data-href=\"http:\/\/www.barackobama.com\/stories\/gun-violence\/14073\/\" data-ref=\"fb_like_btn\" data-send=\"false\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"100\" data-show-faces=\"false\"><\/div>\n        <\/li>\n        <li class=\"twitter\">\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/share\" class=\"twitter-share-button\" data-text=\"Read Sami R.'s story about Gun Violence, then read more from Obama supporters all over.\" data-url=\"http:\/\/www.barackobama.com\/stories\/gun-violence\/14073\/?source=tweet_btn\" data-related=\"BarackObama\">Tweet<\/a>\n        <\/li>\n        <li class=\"email\">\n            <a href=\"mailto:?&amp;subject=You%20should%20read%20this%20story%20about%20Gun+Violence&amp;body=Hey%20--%0A%20%0AI%20just%20read%20Sami%20R.%20from%20Saint%20Louis%20Park%2C%20MN%E2%80%99s%20story%20about%20Gun%20Violence%20and%20supporting%20President%20Obama.%0A%20%0ACheck%20it%20out%20on%20barackobama.com%20at%202012%20Stories%3A%0A%20%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.barackobama.com%2Fstories%2Fgun-violence%2F14073%2F%3Fsource%3Dstories_EMS%0A%20%0AIf%20you%20have%20a%20story%20about%20why%20you%20support%20the%20President%2C%20you%20can%20share%20it%2C%20too.%0A%20%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.barackobama.com%2Fstories%2Fshare-your-story%0A%0AThanks.\" title=\"Share via Email\">Share via Email<\/a>\n        <\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n<\/nav>","gun-violence_14366":"<div class=\"content\">\n    <div class=\"awesome\" data-campaign=\"gun-violence\" data-story-id=\"14366\">66<\/div>\n    <h2 class=\"name\">Michael M.<\/h2>\n    <h3 class=\"location\">New Bern, NC<\/h3>\n    <section class=\"full-text\">\n        <p class=\"summary\">\n            I am a Marine, and the argument my coworkers make is that violence will happen if guns are outlawed, so why do anything.  I disagree.  If I have to choose between my loved one being shot with a pistol or an assault rifle, I choose pistol.  If I have to choose between 9 rounds or 15, I choose 9.  If I have to choose between a pistol or a knife, I choose a knife.  I hope this never happens to a loved one, but I wish we would realize that guns really are a problem.\n        <\/p>\n    <\/section>\n<\/div><nav class=\"sharing\">\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"facebook\">\n            <div class=\"fb-like\" data-href=\"http:\/\/www.barackobama.com\/stories\/gun-violence\/14366\/\" data-ref=\"fb_like_btn\" data-send=\"false\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"100\" data-show-faces=\"false\"><\/div>\n        <\/li>\n        <li class=\"twitter\">\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/share\" class=\"twitter-share-button\" data-text=\"Read Michael M.'s story about Gun Violence, then read more from Obama supporters all over.\" data-url=\"http:\/\/www.barackobama.com\/stories\/gun-violence\/14366\/?source=tweet_btn\" data-related=\"BarackObama\">Tweet<\/a>\n        <\/li>\n        <li class=\"email\">\n            <a href=\"mailto:?&amp;subject=You%20should%20read%20this%20story%20about%20Gun+Violence&amp;body=Hey%20--%0A%20%0AI%20just%20read%20Michael%20M.%20from%20New%20Bern%2C%20NC%E2%80%99s%20story%20about%20Gun%20Violence%20and%20supporting%20President%20Obama.%0A%20%0ACheck%20it%20out%20on%20barackobama.com%20at%202012%20Stories%3A%0A%20%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.barackobama.com%2Fstories%2Fgun-violence%2F14366%2F%3Fsource%3Dstories_EMS%0A%20%0AIf%20you%20have%20a%20story%20about%20why%20you%20support%20the%20President%2C%20you%20can%20share%20it%2C%20too.%0A%20%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.barackobama.com%2Fstories%2Fshare-your-story%0A%0AThanks.\" title=\"Share via Email\">Share via Email<\/a>\n        <\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n<\/nav>","gun-violence_28241":"