before, thrust into the spotlight alongside of Columbine and Virginia Tech. That's why I march for gun control. That's why I fight. Because I am Newtown Strong. \n        <\/p>\n    <\/section>\n<\/div><nav class=\"sharing\">\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"facebook\">\n            <div class=\"fb-like\" data-href=\"http:\/\/www.barackobama.com\/stories\/gun-violence\/41387\/\" data-ref=\"fb_like_btn\" data-send=\"false\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"100\" data-show-faces=\"false\"><\/div>\n        <\/li>\n        <li class=\"twitter\">\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/share\" class=\"twitter-share-button\" data-text=\"Read Mary H.'s story about Gun Violence, then read more from Obama supporters all over.\" data-url=\"http:\/\/www.barackobama.com\/stories\/gun-violence\/41387\/?source=tweet_btn\" data-related=\"BarackObama\">Tweet<\/a>\n        <\/li>\n        <li class=\"email\">\n            <a href=\"mailto:?&amp;subject=You%20should%20read%20this%20story%20about%20Gun+Violence&amp;body=Hey%20--%0A%20%0AI%20just%20read%20Mary%20H.%20from%20Newtown%2C%20CT%E2%80%99s%20story%20about%20Gun%20Violence%20and%20supporting%20President%20Obama.%0A%20%0ACheck%20it%20out%20on%20barackobama.com%20at%202012%20Stories%3A%0A%20%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.barackobama.com%2Fstories%2Fgun-violence%2F41387%2F%3Fsource%3Dstories_EMS%0A%20%0AIf%20you%20have%20a%20story%20about%20why%20you%20support%20the%20President%2C%20you%20can%20share%20it%2C%20too.%0A%20%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.barackobama.com%2Fstories%2Fshare-your-story%0A%0AThanks.\" title=\"Share via Email\">Share via Email<\/a>\n        <\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n<\/nav>","gun-violence_14760":"<div class=\"content\">\n    <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>This was me at the five year memorial @<a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/niulive\">niulive<\/a>, paying respect to my classmates lost that day. <a href=\"http:\/\/t.co\/CJgFkpO2\" title=\"http:\/\/twitter.com\/PatrickKorellis\/status\/304015907292868609\/photo\/1