my uncle fatally and accidentally shot his baby brother while out hunting.   &lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;How am I supposed to console my class of kindergartners over a classmate's death and tell them that they are safe, when I don't even believe it myself?&lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;Guns hurt people.  Guns hurt innocent people.  Guns create innocent victims.  \n        <\/p>\n    <\/section>\n<\/div><nav class=\"sharing\">\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"facebook\">\n            <div class=\"fb-like\" data-href=\"http:\/\/www.barackobama.com\/stories\/gun-violence\/14082\/\" data-ref=\"fb_like_btn\" data-send=\"false\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"100\" data-show-faces=\"false\"><\/div>\n        <\/li>\n        <li class=\"twitter\">\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/share\" class=\"twitter-share-button\" data-text=\"Read Pang X.'s story about Gun Violence, then read more from Obama supporters all over.\" data-url=\"http:\/\/www.barackobama.com\/stories\/gun-violence\/14082\/?source=tweet_btn\" data-related=\"BarackObama\">Tweet<\/a>\n        <\/li>\n        <li class=\"email\">\n            <a href=\"mailto:?&amp;subject=You%20should%20read%20this%20story%20about%20Gun+Violence&amp;body=Hey%20--%0A%20%0AI%20just%20read%20Pang%20X.%20from%20Little%20Canada%2C%20MN%E2%80%99s%20story%20about%20Gun%20Violence%20and%20supporting%20President%20Obama.%0A%20%0ACheck%20it%20out%20on%20barackobama.com%20at%202012%20Stories%3A%0A%20%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.barackobama.com%2Fstories%2Fgun-violence%2F14082%2F%3Fsource%3Dstories_EMS%0A%20%0AIf%20you%20have%20a%20story%20about%20why%20you%20support%20the%20President%2C%20you%20can%20share%20it%2C%20too.%0A%20%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.barackobama.com%2Fstories%2Fshare-your-story%0A%0AThanks.\" title=\"Share via Email\">Share via Email<\/a>\n        <\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n<\/nav>","gun-violence_15610":"<div class=\"content\">\n    <div class=\"awesome\" data-campaign=\"gun-violence\" data-story-id=\"15610\">47<\/div>\n    <h2